lead_paragraph: Kuwait is not a "free-rider" in U.S.-led campaigns against terrorism and other threats, a senior Kuwaiti security official said on Thursday, rejecting comments by President Barack Obama critical of some U.S. allies.

headline.main: Kuwait Security Chief to Obama: We're Not Free-Riders
headline.print_headline: Kuwait Security Chief to Obama: We're Not Free-Riders
